name: Reality game
description:
Existence in many realities as a new form of life, play as a practice of endless actions, where the form of the body refers to the material in a digital format.
AR Digital kinetic sculpture created in VR Oculus Medium, animation in Blender.
You can see this in AR if you go to this page from your smartphone and press the AR button in the lower left corner. 
By Vlas Belov Website: http://vlasbelov.tilda.ws/
